\par\pard\plain \ql\ltrch\loch {\f1\fs24\b1\i0 18}{\f0\fs24\b0\i0  }{\f0\fs24\b0\i0 But someone will say, \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93You have faith and I have works.\u8221\'94 Show me your faith apart from your works, and I will show you my faith by my works. }
